com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.configuration

Interface DraftsTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Drafts
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DraftsStub

    public interface DraftsTypes
    The Drafts interface provides methods to manage cluster configuration drafts. This interface was added in vSphere API 8.0.2.0.
